title: EP.59: JAIRE VS DIGGS, STEELERS FUTURE, TRADES, AND MUCH MORE!
description: "Don't think about it too much too much too muuuuuuch" is all packers fans can do at this point. A big trade or signing is our only hope. Is it too late to get Davante Adams back? Steelers fans are also doomed for this season as we have seen right now these QBs are not gonna get the job done this year. It looks like the super bowl chase is down to the Eagles, Vikings, Bills, and Chiefs with a few others if they get hot at the right time. Tune in for more!
dc:creator: Griffin Proctor & Joe Jokonya
